      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/crypto-investment-products-see-third-straight-week-of-outflows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数字资产投资产品连续第三周出现资金流出，但提款速度有所放缓，这可能是投资者情绪发生转变的结果。]]></description>
